'''Jaaruls Street''' was a road in [[Cuipernam]], the [[Capital/Legends|capital city]] of [[Ansion/Legends|Ansion]]. It was the location on an unnamed building in which [[Kyakhta]] and [[Bulgan]], the clanless [[Ansionian]] enforcers of [[Soergg Vosadii Bezhin|Soergg]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]], took the [[Kidnapping of Barriss Offee|kidnapped]] [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Padawan/Legends|Padawan]] [[Barriss Offee/Legends|Barriss Offee]] in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], during the Jedi [[Border dispute on Ansion/Legends|mission to Ansion]].

